texts.text: >4 years ago.
Hey, I'm back. Here's your cream bun.
Oh, awesome!
I never thought the nurse call button would turn me into your butler...
Ah, but it's so handy. Think of it as a friendly visit too.
You know I'm on the clock.
But I never thought you'd end up here with me as your attending.
Hey. This thing's expiration date.
Is it expired?
No.
It has more time than I do...
Oh...

*Laugh*
That really killed your mood.
You're such a jerk.
It's just the way I am.
Damn, this is so good.
I'm glad. Just tell me when you want another one...
Nah, I'll have someone else get it.
It's fine. I don't mind...
>Now.
>Everyone steps into the morgue.
Oh... It's different when there are real dead people around...
A real morgue is brighter than I thought it would be too...
>Spirits are present all over the room.
Master... Murmur...
Duke...
>You see a well-clad knight surrounded by dead spirits.
Oh... Is that Murmur...?
Everyone, stay sharp.
We finally found him. Murmur.
Ah, the one that broke the seal. For that I give my thanks.
But I am still burdened by the fact that your ritual left me incomplete.
What are you doing here?
Are you the one attacking people using these spirits?
Mind your tongue, child... Do you not know who you are speaking to?
Nonetheless, I am the one commanding these spirits.
But why...?!
Oh, to a muster an army of the dead for "him" of course.
To end those blasted angels once and for all.
Is that all? Human.
You can call for the spirits of the dead, yes?
Then please let me see my dead lover...!
You... You had a lover?
There there.
I have no time for such frivolous nonsense.
Your contract can wait until after I have raised my new army.
However, this may take years.
But...
And Gemori. Are you not one of "his" servants as well?
How did you let yourself fall under the control of these humans?
I am a demon that can procure a woman's love... Here to serve this boy.
And it would be wise to keep your head down while "he" is away.
Pathetic. I am preparing for the day "he" makes his return.
And if you make too many enemies along the way?
Then there is nothing to do but fell them one by one!
G-get ready...!
>Suddenly, Yu lunges at Murmur's legs.
Hurry! While I hold him down...
What are you doing?! Hold on! Devil Download!
Ah, I see. Demon users. You will make fine additions to this army.
Go my spirits!
You... Die... Murmur... Serve...
Too late. Headshot!
*Groan*
This is nothing compared to any zombie game.
And while she's on a roll... Devil Download!
*Groan*
Nothing I haven't seen before in a movie.
You're up, Newbie!
Bring the heat.
Play it cool.
*Groan*
So many spirits at once... This is getting good!
*Groan*
Your stance, aim and strategy. All perfect marks.
I knew you had a talent for this.
Ah. You have more of a spine than I expected...!
*Scream*
Doctor?!
>Murmur grabs Dr. Kayama by her collar.
This wench will do nicely. Let those you let die arise once more.
>As Murmur speaks, Dr. Kayama's eyes roll into the back of her head.
Uh...
Dr. Kayama! Are you okay?!
This is bad! So many spirits...
It... Hurts... Doctor...
Doctor... Help...
These spirits... Kurashima... Yamaguchi...
Doctor... Why...? Why didn't you help me...?
There... There was nothing I could do... Forgive me...
It hurts... It hurts... I'm... Scared...
I'm... Dying...? I don't want to die...!
No... No...
Doctor! Hang on!
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
>Dr. Kayama cries as she mumbles and is lifted into the air.
Doctor! Wake up!
I'm sorry. He died. She died. They died. They all died. All of them.
Dr. Kayama! Dr. Kayama!
Murmur! What did you do?!
I am raising the spirits of those she let die is all.
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorrrrrrryyy...
Dr. Kayama would never do anything like that!
She is repenting for her sins. And these spirits seem alive and well.
You... Die...!
Ahh...!
They're way stronger than before...! Why?
By bringing her trauma to the surface,
they become increasingly more powerful.
*Twitch*
Her mind will break in due time.
She will no longer be herself if we do not save her soon.
What will you do, devil users?
Please! Kick that thing's ass!
Of course. We need to move as a unit!
